Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我听不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了船长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.38,0:00:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.17,0:00:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.51,0:00:34.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:34.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.30,0:00:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:49.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1179.518,406)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:54.95,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}蟹堡塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:57.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(233.101,458.667)\frz30.02}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:59.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:57.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(493.463,720.667)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(359.882,414.001)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:59.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(501.478,667.334)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(429.344,542)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我本来是准备好要炸薯条的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, I was all ready to drain the fries
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是我把薯条炸得有点太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I cooked the fries slightly too long
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.24,0:01:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.00,0:01:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是薯条有了奇怪扭曲的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So here's where the bizarre twist comes in
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.34,0:01:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.92,0:01:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没有炸过头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They weren't overcooked at all
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.72,0:01:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.93,0:01:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.77,0:01:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡塔现在正式开门营业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Towers is now open for business
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:27.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(786.79,128.667)}盛大开业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:27.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(794.805,419.334)}蟹堡塔
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么要盖酒店啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:29.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you build a hotel, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.05,0:01:30.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问得正好  小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:30.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you asked, son
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.23,0:01:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记不记得我先前去参加快餐大会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember when I went to that fast food convention
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(455.51,307.333)}酒店
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.70,0:01:34.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住进了家豪华酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:34.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and stayed in that fancy hotel?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我住的房间可漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had a beautiful room
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,员工特别的友好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The employees were so friendly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们无微不至地关照我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They catered to me every whim
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算我要求很丢脸也照办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no matter how demeaning it was
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为他们的生活有一条规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:47.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because they lived by a code
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.37,0:01:51.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而它正镌刻在壮丽火炉之上的黄金中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:49.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that code was engraved in fine gold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,above the grand fireplace
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.86,0:01:57.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(800.111,894)}我们绝不拒绝客人的请求\N连最荒唐的都一样
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything was perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.39,0:02:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿到账单就不完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until I got the bill
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(923.043,784.667)}收银员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:02.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(987.161,352.667)}账单
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们不管什么都收我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They charged me for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:03.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410.093,451.334)}共计
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.37,0:02:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汉堡一个还二十五块
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,$25.00 for a hamburger
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(536.138,202)}客房
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(511.435,350)}泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594.883,508)}桑拿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(840.556,665.333)}汉堡
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是连个垃圾汉堡都能收那么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If they could charge that much for a lousy burger
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.65,0:02:16.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就想想我能靠垃圾蟹黄堡收多少钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,imagine how much
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could charge for a lousy Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.39,0:02:19.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是  蟹堡塔诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:19.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And thus, the Krusty Towers was born
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村怎么会有人住酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would anyone stay at a hotel in Bikini Bottom?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里虽然风景好  但是很偏僻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's in the middle of scenic nowhere
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这就只能被水母蛰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to do but get stung by jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:32.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come inside
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漂不漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新来的酒店员工在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are all the new hotel employees?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一个来酒店的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me first hotel guest
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我把他引进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch me reel him in
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临蟹堡塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Krusty Towers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的格言是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where our motto is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们绝不拒绝客人的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"We shall never deny a guest
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连最荒唐的都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even the most ridiculous request"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.87,0:02:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份双层蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like a double Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不加洋葱  多加腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with no onions and extra pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你要蟹黄堡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得租间房间还有订购客房服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have to rent a room, and order room service
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我午餐只能吃一个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've only got an hour for lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你啊  引流引得可真是专业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, you reeled that one in like a pro
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来做前台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you run the front desk
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like a Krabby Patty, please
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里现在是家酒店了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a hotel now
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你要蟹黄堡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得租间房间还有订购客房服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll have to get a room, and order room service
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡跟一间房间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty and one room
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要加奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡上也可以加奶酪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And can I get cheese on the Krabby Patty, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你家离这才四百码远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you only live 400 yards away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛要来住酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to check into a hotel?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.68,0:03:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候我就只是想要远离坐世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I just need to get away from it all
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这酒店什么都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This hotel has everything
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.55,0:03:38.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:38.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,签登记簿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now sign the register
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都不知道还有考试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't know there would be a test
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没念好书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't study
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你只要签好名就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:46.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, all you have to do is write your name
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.99,0:03:48.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:48.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能别看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.21,0:03:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't look
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.09,0:03:58.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:58.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Done
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close enough
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,房门钥匙给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your room key
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要帮手来帮忙提包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll need some help with my bags
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪来的包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you have bags?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚才才知道这里是酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just found out this is a hotel
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这里是酒店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a hotel?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把派大星跟他包带到他房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take Patrick and his bags to his room
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我蟹黄堡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about my Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给人家拿蟹黄堡去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And bring him a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你把派大星的包提到他房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you can take Patrick's bags up to his room
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你去做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you go make the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点点体力活就怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Afraid of a little manual labor?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是章鱼哥  我得干活谋生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I'm Squidward, and I have to work for a living"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.96,0:04:36.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:36.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们走  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这部电梯只能客人用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This elevator is for guests only
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你用员工电梯去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take the employee elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:51.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(268.497,382)}员工电梯
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你包里什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's in these bags?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rocks?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.86,0:05:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are rocks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你包里怎么全是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why is your suitcase full of rocks?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又没教你怎么过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't tell you how to live your life
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  你房间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here's your room
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,入住愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your stay
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个啥我还会再给的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and there will be more where that came from
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的蟹黄堡  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your Krabby Patty, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  石头挺酷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, cool rock
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  我的大善人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you are, my good man
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.87,0:05:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个啥我会再给不少的  我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's plenty more where that came from, my good friend
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.17,0:05:40.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:40.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢我蟹黄堡上的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't like crusts on my sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个是面包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a bun
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来就全都是皮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all crust
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要怎么把面包上的皮给弄掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to cut the crust off a bun?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,削掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peel it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.29,0:05:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,客房服务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Room service
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你点的五十份蟹黄堡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the 50 Krabby Patties you ordered
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可不可以再给我做件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you do one more thing for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你叫海绵宝宝做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能为你效劳吗  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How may I serve you, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要你来跟我一起吃掉这些蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you to eat these Krabby Patties with me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.15,0:06:13.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:13.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.81,0:06:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星要你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick needs your help
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他怎么不提前问我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he ask me
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都好不容易一路走下楼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before I walked all the way downstairs?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他本来说他不想打扰到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He said he didn't want to bother you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而他又忘了这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:22.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he got over it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  这简直荒唐得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, this is ridiculous
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星的要求完完全全不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's being completely unreasonable
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他爱怎么不合理就可以怎么不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He can be as unreasonable as he wants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看牌匾  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The plaque, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.16,0:06:41.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看牌匾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:41.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The plaque
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不拒绝客人的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deny no guest
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, hello, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要章鱼哥马上过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:50.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need Squidward to come up right away?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会马上到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll be right there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A bubble bath?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我凭什么要给你洗泡泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would I give you a bubble bath?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为蟹老板说你会给我洗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, because Mr. Krabs said you would
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.57,0:07:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要把我的后背擦得特别光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be sure to make my back extra shiny clean
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:05.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:07.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had enough
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马桶又堵着了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The toilet's backed up again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能坐那部电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't take that elevator
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是员工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're an employee
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不当了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I quit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:17.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quit?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.78,0:07:18.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能辞职啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:18.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't quit
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临蟹堡塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Krusty Towers
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请来一间房  要顶楼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One room, please, on the top floor
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你以为你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要度假
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a vacation
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.54,0:07:34.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我劳累过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:34.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm overworked
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.01,0:07:38.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,何况蟹堡塔最适合放松了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:38.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And what better place to relax than Krusty Towers
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.14,0:07:41.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里绝不拒绝客人的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:41.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where we shall never deny a guest
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.18,0:07:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连最荒唐的都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even the most ridiculous request
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没必要把房间租给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have to rent you a room
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.05,0:07:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有现金
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got cash
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,房门钥匙给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your room key
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  把我东西提到我房间里去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, carry my things to my room
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.58,0:07:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  客人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, guest sir
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以把我抱到我房间里去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you can carry me to my room
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我凭什么要那么干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And why in tarnation would I do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你长着好端端的四条腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got four legs that aren't broken
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.71,0:08:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看牌匾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The plaque
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698.627,918)}我们绝不拒绝客人的请求\N连最荒唐的都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(1174.174,187.333)}17{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}层
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真可惜坐不了电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad we couldn't take the elevator
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是电梯只让客人坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it is for guests only
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你就只是一员工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you are an employee
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.54,0:08:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的房间  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your room, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想订购客房服务了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'd like to order room service
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要加奶酪  脚趾甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with cheese, toenail clippings
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有鼻毛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and nose hairs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是在开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要它五秒钟就送来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I want it here in five seconds
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.10,0:08:27.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:27.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you are, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  你的恶心三明治买到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you got your stinky sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now eat it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不吃这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to eat this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是以为我会吃  你就是痴心妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're out of your mind if you think I'm going to eat that
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个蟹黄堡其实并没有完全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not really a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加了奶酪  脚趾甲跟鼻毛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with cheese, toenails and nose hair
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白你意思了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:47.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I get you, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶酪都用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We were all out of cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送一打饼干过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Send up a dozen cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要有从前我妈做的那味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like mother used to make
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手工饼干来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your homemade cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全没有我妈从前做的那味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These don't taste anything like mom used to make
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你妈是怎么做的饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, how did your mother make 'em?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.02,0:09:20.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问我妈去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:20.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ask my mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:22.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(917.7,680.667)}章鱼夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:22.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(583.748,590)}邮件
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有用  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No good, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我来  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.02,0:09:47.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:47.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我待洗衣物放进了后备厢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that me laundry is in the trunk
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你完全就能坐前边的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's room for you to sit up front
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们去烤饼干吧  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go bake some cookies, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.53,0:09:55.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:55.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真有我妈以前做的那味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,These are just like mother used to make
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望我妈厨艺能更好点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wish mom was a better cook
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你满意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you're all taken care of
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就一个小小的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just one teensy, tiny problem
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这房间太丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This room is hideous
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去重新设计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Redesign it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神十四世的风格倒不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neptune the 14th would be nice
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.30,0:10:10.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:10.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们绝不拒绝客人的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"We shall never deny a guest
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连最荒唐的都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even the most ridiculous request"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.30,0:10:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这房间就跟原先的一模一样啊这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This room is exactly the same as when we started
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重回基础最好不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing like getting back to the basics
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们出去吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们临走前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Before you leave
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去游个泳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to go swimming
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泳池在外头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pool is out back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯了吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不去外头游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not going outside to swim
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on in
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水很舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The water's fine
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有什么又傻又不合理的要求吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything else stupid and unreasonable that you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要我帮你嚼食物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't need me to chew your food for you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是不要拿我脊椎给你做抓背器了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or make you a back scratcher out of my own spine?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是还不要扑灭太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or maybe extinguish the sun
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你眼睛不被光照到是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so the light don't get in your eyes?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必  我很满意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm good
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.22,0:11:03.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:03.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有室内游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An indoor pool
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方可真是高档
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炮弹来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cannonball
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fn@Adobe 黑体 Std R\frz270\pos(434.137,707.333)}医院
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盖酒店打一开始就是个馊主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That hotel was a bad idea from the start
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来那是酒店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was a hotel?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的账单  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your bill, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要一万五
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,$15,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.86\pos(110.872,307.333)}床
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.86\pos(129.573,398)}绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.86\pos(183.005,480.667)}药物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.86\pos(183.005,592.667)}病房服务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.86\pos(709.313,488.667)}共计
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该不会要心脏病发作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not going to have a heart attack, are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么会有这么贵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not at these prices
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酒店不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget hotels
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医院的架子才是放钱的好她方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This hospital racket is where the money is
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来这是家医院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a hospital?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收拾行李  小伙子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pack your bags, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要去上医学院了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to medical school
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.07,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\fsp50}泡芙老师\N{\fs40} \N{\fs175}失业了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(233.101,458.667)\frz30.02}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:12:01.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(506.821,736.667)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(378.583,430.001)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(509.493,678.001)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.02\pos(429.344,542)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(653.21,547.333)}泡芙老师\N滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  泡芙女士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是费兹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Mr. Fitz
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.33,0:12:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是驾校教练评审机构的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I represent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Voting Teachers Accreditation Bureau
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you know
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的教练证即将到期  需要更新
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your teaching certificate is up for renewal
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是我们注意到这一班里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,However, we've noticed there have been
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有异常多的不及格案例出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an unusually large amount
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of failings from this classroom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.27,0:12:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这么多年的教学生涯里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In all my years of teaching
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教过的班级只有一个学生不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,only one student has failed my class
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.54,0:12:29.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是没错  可是他有1258056次不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:29.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, but he's failed 1,258,056 times
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朽木不可雕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unteachable
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.23,0:12:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能因为教练不力而去责备学生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We cannot blame the students
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the incompetence of the teacher
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好开船了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to drive
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好迎接我的驾考了吗  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for my driving test today, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.73,0:12:51.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙女士  如果海绵宝宝这次又挂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:51.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mrs. Puff, if SpongeBob fails this test
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.32,0:12:54.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须换掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:54.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you will be replaced
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  来给费兹先生示范一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, SpongeBob, let's demonstrate for Mr. Fitz
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在滑浪学校里教你的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everything I've taught you in boating school
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.55,0:13:05.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开船前要做的第一件事是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:05.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what's the first thing we do before we start boating?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,系好安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seatbelt-a-rooni
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.01,0:13:07.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:07.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One second
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then what do you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发动引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Start the engine?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.02,0:13:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.79,0:13:25.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:25.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drive the boat
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这回及格了吗  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I pass this time, Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You failed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不及格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I failed?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挂的并不是你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is not you that's failed, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.24,0:13:44.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挂的是泡芙老师才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:44.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Mrs. Puff that's failed you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的教练职务被免除了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are relieved of your teaching duties
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不用再教海绵宝宝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't be teaching SpongeBob anymore?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.02,0:13:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为不会有这么一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought this day would never come
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路走好吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a nice life
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free at last
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(674.583,542)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我害泡芙老师失业了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:17.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got Mrs. Puff fired
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好  不中用的同学们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, worthless students
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(760.074,774)}泡芙老师
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你们的新教练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your new instructor
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我课上挂科的就没有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one's ever failed my class
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's lived through it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以向你们保证  接下来这四周
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can assure you, these next four weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.39,0:14:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会是你们痛苦人生中最悲惨的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will be the worst years of your miserable lives
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的脊椎会断掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your spines will break
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.15,0:14:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的牙齿会疼死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your teeth will ache
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们的眼睛会充满血丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your eyes will be bloodshot
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们最后不是毕业风光开船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will drive out of this school in style
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.93,0:14:53.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是挂科坐着奶奶的篮子被推出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:53.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or you will be carted out in your granny's handbasket
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.90,0:14:56.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每个人都要遵守好班规
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:56.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone will follow the rules of the class
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一条班规  严禁讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First rule: no talking
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that mean
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.13,0:15:05.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二条班规  班上严禁吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:05.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Second rule: no eating in my class
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁想要吃夹心糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would anyone care for a bon-bon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1107.384,840.667)}夹心糖
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来颗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll eat one
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱挑哪个挑哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick your favorite
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's it taste?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.62,0:15:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道可不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a delightful taste sensation
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,班上严禁吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No eating in my classroom
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.36,0:15:30.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果有人有勇气待在这班上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:30.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, if anyone else is man enough to stay in this class
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么说你很有勇气了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're the man
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.45,0:15:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是要来学开船的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to learn how to drive or what?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.87,0:15:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.66,0:15:40.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好去开船了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:40.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to drive
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.71,0:15:43.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备过驾考  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:43.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for my test, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还不算准备好开船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not ready to drive yet--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要先学会那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until you learn that first
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.46,0:15:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是有史以来最累人的驾驶训练道路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the most grueling driving course ever devised
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.24,0:15:56.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要掌握每个转弯突起跟裂缝的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:56.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will learn every turn, bump and crack on it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但要先从爬开始学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll start out crawling it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.21,0:15:58.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:15:58.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crawl?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hup two, hup two
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,左转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Left turn
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crack
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.21,0:16:05.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,突起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:05.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bump
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.88,0:16:06.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,半毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:06.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有半毛钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, a nickel
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意看路  学员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes on the road, cadet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pebble
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真是为你感到羞耻  学员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:36.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of you, cadet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然能被一个小小的石块绊倒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tripped up by a wee pebble
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在我班上是要学什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you supposed to be learning in my class?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.91,0:16:42.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是开船  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:42.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How to drive, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Affirmative
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但在你学会开船之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But before you learn to drive
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须要学会爬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you must learn to crawl
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后学会走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then you learn to walk
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后学会跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then you learn to run
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.15,0:16:55.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但在你学会走之前  必须先学会爬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:55.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But before you learn to walk, you must learn to crawl
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在给我爬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to crawl
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在上路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get out there
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(559.703,787.333)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.39,0:17:22.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每个好司机都得里里外外摸清他的船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every good boater
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,needs to know his vehicle inside and out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去拆了那艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go take that boat apart
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是不错  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, son
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再装回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put it back together again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll be easy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.11,0:17:34.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:34.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.89,0:17:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把这东西放到那玩意上去然后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just put the jing-a-mahoos on the poo-hickey and, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能要那么几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might need a couple of minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:43.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's ready, Sarge
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的水母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumping jellyfish
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(957.774,416.667)}终点线
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.72,0:17:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch for pedestrians
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,检查后视镜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check mirrors
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.13,0:17:59.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好限速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:17:59.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Observe that speed limit
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,注意行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:01.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch for pedestrians
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, um
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how'd I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you do?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.28,0:18:22.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不去问这行人的碎尸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:22.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the shattered remains of this pedestrian
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how you did?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对这道路的前后边角都了如指掌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:28.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I know this course forward, backward and sideways
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.66,0:18:29.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以去开船了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:29.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Am I ready to get behind the wheel?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没到那程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not quite
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴眼罩来做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now do it blindfolded
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.59,0:18:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,几天后
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1003
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,003
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1004
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,004
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1005
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,005
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,143号石块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pebble number 143
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不会再绊到我的了  143号石块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will not trip me up again, pebble number 143
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1006
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,006
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1007
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,007
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1008
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,008
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿了个火腿三明治的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old lady with a ham sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1009
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,009
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1010
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,010
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1011
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,011
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.35,0:18:56.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1012
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:56.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1,012
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.48,0:18:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one th
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以准备好去开船了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're ready to get behind the wheel
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.01,0:19:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.58,0:19:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.29,0:19:07.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来查验你学习成果了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:07.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see what I taught you, laddie
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.66,0:19:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命长官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在143号石块处左转
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Left turn at pebble number 143
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿球的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kid with a ball
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice driving
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到前边去侧方停车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now parallel park up ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very good
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.01,0:19:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.96,0:19:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给费兹先生查验成果的时刻已经来到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the time has come to show Mr. Fitz what you learned
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.02,0:19:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命长官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一步  安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step one: seat belts
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做的好  学员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excellent work, cadet
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一步是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二步是  发动引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step two would be: ignite engine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:40.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step three
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第三步是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step three would be
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴眼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,engage blindfold
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.87,0:19:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.46,0:19:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴眼罩不可以开船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't drive a boat with a blindfold on
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.32,0:19:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样子犯法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's illegal
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我不戴眼罩开不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I can't do it without a blindfold
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drive, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快开啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1053.952,518)}汽油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1045.937,878)}易燃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1307.755,691.333)}危险
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mayday
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已驶离道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're off course
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我内心可舒坦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel so serene
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.54,0:20:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于可以远离那杀人狂魔海绵宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,now that I'm away from that homicidal maniac, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刹车  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The brake, son
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命长官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:46.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄好了  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:49.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, sir--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拧掉两颗螺栓就拆下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all I had to do was unscrew two little bolts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要逼停这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stop this thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我跟老婆说我爱她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell my wife I love her
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:03.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come get some
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.28,0:21:08.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.28,0:21:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.83,0:21:10.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:10.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉派大星  我没法抽空陪你聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Patrick, I can't stop to talk right now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看不到东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pants
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看不到东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.02,0:21:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我及格了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I pass?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.92,0:21:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是驾考有毁灭城市这个模块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.92,0:21:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if there was a "destroy the city" part of the test
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.53,0:21:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你早及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you would have
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某些人可真是神经质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The nerve of some people
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.84,0:21:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又挂科了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you failed again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.27,0:21:55.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连我们最好的教练都不能教好你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:55.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even our finest instructor could not teach you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.72,0:21:58.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙女士  你又被录用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.72,0:21:58.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff, you're hired again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.17,0:22:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.16,0:22:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真抱歉我朽木不可雕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm "unteachable"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(829.536,339.333)}优等
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.47,0:22:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,费兹先生把我教练证拿回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fitz gave me my teaching certificate back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.89,0:22:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且你的档案也被炸没了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And your dossier was destroyed in the explosion
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你差不多从来没不及格过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So it's as if you never failed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.74,0:22:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个回归礼物要送你  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got you a "welcome back" gift, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.69,0:22:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把所有碎片找出来粘回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found all the pieces and glued them back together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(800.148,934)}泡芙老师
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.19,0:22:25.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证我绝不会再来考个一百万次了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:25.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise it won't take me a million tries thistime
